@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = v1
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos((v2 + 0.88 + tmp + 0.05)))
    v0 = wp.abs(v2)
    v2 = v0
    v2 = (0.42 / ((v2 + 0.71 * v0 + 0.36) / (v2 + 0.32 / v2 + 0.65)))
    tmp = (v0 * (v1 + (v2 + 0.57 / v0 + 0.48)))
    data[tid] = v0
